stardust on the sage is a 1942 american western film directed by joseph kane and written by robert creighton williams . the film stars william boyd , andy clyde , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry davenport , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , harry dean stanton , and john wayne . the film was released on january 28 , 1942 , by republic pictures .